{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>개발환경 설정하기</h1>\n<h2>Tools</h2>\n<h3>iTerm2</h3>\n<p>이 <a href=\"https://www.iterm2.com/\">링크</a>에서 다운받을 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3>homebrew</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://brew.sh/index_ko\">맥용 패키지 관리도구</a> 입니다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">/usr/bin/ruby -e <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>zsh</h3>\n<p>brew 를 이용해 <a href=\"https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/wiki/Installing-ZSH\">zsh를 설치</a>합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> zsh zsh-completions</code></pre></div>\n<p>기본 shell 을 zsh 로 변경합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">chsh -s /bin/zsh</code></pre></div>\n<h3>oh-my-zsh</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/\">oh-my-zsh</a>를 설치합니다. curl 또는 wget을 이용하여 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># curl</span>\n\nsh -c <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># wget</span>\n\nsh -c <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">wget</span> https://raw.githubusercontent.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3><a href=\"https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting\">zsh-syntax-highlighting</a></h3>\n<p>zsh 의 syntax highlighting 도구를 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> zsh-syntax-highlighting</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">~/.zshrc</code>의 plugins 항목에 <code class=\"language-text\">zsh-syntax-highlighting</code>을 추가합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">plugins<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> zsh-syntax-highlighting<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>zsh를 재실행하면 적용됩니다.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://github.com/athityakumar/colorls#installation\">colorls</a></h3>\n<p>ruby를 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> ruby</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gem</code>을 이용하여 colorls를 설치합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">gem <span class=\"token function\">install</span> colorls</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">~/.zshrc</code>에 alias를 추가합니다. (기존 ls를 대체하기 위해 ls alias도 지정합니다.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">alias</span> ls<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"colorls\"</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">alias</span> ll<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"colorls -al\"</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">alias</span> lc<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"colorls -lA --sd\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Fonts</h2>\n<p>코드를 미려하게 표현해줄 폰트를 설치합니다.</p>\n<h3>FiraFont</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/3a8948f34284f378ead7af5846aa432035c687ad/687474703a2f2f732e746f6e736b792e6d652f696d67732f666972615f636f64655f6c6f676f2e737667\" alt=\"firacode sample\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/tonsky/FiraCode\">github</a> 페이지를 통해 다운로드 링크를 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3>NerdFonts</h3>\n<p>iconic font 입니다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/raw/master/images/sankey-glyphs-combined-diagram.svg?sanitize=true\" alt=\"nerdfonts\"></p>\n<p>github 페이지를 통해 설치방법을 안내받을 수 있으며, homebrew를 사용하는 경우 아래의 코드로 설치할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew tap caskroom/fonts\nbrew cask <span class=\"token function\">install</span> font-hack-nerd-font</code></pre></div>\n<p>iTerm2를 사용하는 경우 Preference > Profiles > Text 에서 Non-ASCII Font 항목을 활성화하고 해당 폰트를 <code class=\"language-text\">Hack Regular Nerd Font</code>로 설정해주셔야 정상적으로 표시됩니다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3d9a0de92a54ccfcf6b5e46c9fc0a1e6/e9e87/iterm2_nerdfont.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 35.79335793357934%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"nerd font with iterms2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3d9a0de92a54ccfcf6b5e46c9fc0a1e6/40fad/iterm2_nerdfont.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3d9a0de92a54ccfcf6b5e46c9fc0a1e6/707e9/iterm2_nerdfont.png 148w,\n/static/3d9a0de92a54ccfcf6b5e46c9fc0a1e6/649e0/iterm2_nerdfont.png 295w,\n/static/3d9a0de92a54ccfcf6b5e46c9fc0a1e6/40fad/iterm2_nerdfont.png 590w,\n/static/3d9a0de92a54ccfcf6b5e46c9fc0a1e6/b3fef/iterm2_nerdfont.png 885w,\n/static/3d9a0de92a54ccfcf6b5e46c9fc0a1e6/e9e87/iterm2_nerdfont.png 1084w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 14, 2019","path":"/dev-environment","title":"Do You Buy New Macbook? Now"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"description":"Advanced Frontend Engineer"}}},"pageContext":{}}